CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: CNB Financial Corp is providing integrated financial solutions, which create value for both consumers and businesses. These solutions encompass deposit accounts, private banking, real estate, commercial, industrial, residential and consumer loans and lines of credit, credit cards, treasury services, online banking, mobile banking, merchant credit card processing, remote deposit and accounts receivable handling. In addition, the corporation provides wealth and asset management services, retirement plans and other employee benefit plans.
